-- Tibco Software reviews strategic, financial alternatives 
-- 
-- Wed Sep 03, 2014 05:34PM EDT
-- None



Sept 3 (Reuters) - Business software maker Tibco Software Inc <TIBX.O> said it is reviewing its strategic and financial alternatives as part of a process initiated by its board on Aug. 16 to maximize shareholder value.

Tibco has formed a special committee of independent directors to undertake the review. The company said it had retained Wilson Sonsini Goodrich & Rosati and Goldman, Sachs & Co to assist in the process. [ID:nMKWdHFVja]